    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a superlative example of the marque, powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six engine featuring individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. The mechanical synchronized engagement of the Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission remains crisp, delivering torque through a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul, rod bearing replacement, and a structural reinforcement of the rear subframe mounting points. The chassis retains its factory-fresh torsional rigidity, complemented by an unblemished exterior and an interior free of typical bolster wear or trim delamination. This is a collector-grade specimen optimized for both longitudinal acceleration and lateral G-force composure.",
      "price": 48500.0,
